/// section bg:muted
h2: Frequently asked questions

col:
  h3: Can I use my own Kafka cluster?
  p: Yes. The SDK is broker-agnostic. The managed Cloud tier runs NATS JetStream under the hood, but the OSS version works with any NATS, Kafka, or Redis Streams backend.

col:
  h3: Is there a free trial for Cloud?
  p: Cloud plans include a 14-day trial with no credit card required. You'll get 10M events to test with before you're charged.

col:
  h3: What counts as an event?
  p: Any publish() call that reaches the broker. Failed attempts before retry exhaustion are not counted.
